== 11. Bg2 ==
White develops the light-squared bishop and prepares to castle short.
From this position, two moves have been played historically: f6 and g5.

[[/11...f6|'''11...f6''']] is the old mainline, defending the knight.

[[/11...g5|'''11...g5''']] is the most popular line nowadays and is considered the best move for Black.


